            "body": "You have the right approach in the namespace update, but a pull request would have to be accepted before any other changes since it's a very disruptive change.\n\nFor an example:\nhttps://github.com/dag/flask-zodb/\n\nI expect the overall namespace upgrade to take a very long time.  I'm pretty sure `easy_install` (pure setuptools) does not exhibit this installation bug, only pip (not sure which version or whether fixed).\n"
